data.Name: Value Select
data.Bio: Maxwell Scott Renner (also known as Value Select) is an American musician, comedian, and occasionally, both. He is also the king of Planet Select, the inventor of Mirth Pop, creator of the hit series' 'I wake up Sad' and 'Shanghai Ballers'. Little is known of the background of this enigmatic gentleman, in fact, some claim he doesn't have a background at all, and instead formed from the infinite abyss of time and space at some point in 2017.
